But still have some error while using cann provider in the onnxruntime。

        'device_id': 1,
        'max_opqueue_num': 10000,
        'arena_extend_strategy': 'kNextPowerOfTwo',

        'do_copy_in_default_stream': True,
    }),
]`

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3061079/215312628-9e95e20f-6fc0-49ce-a217-3a8c112ed96a.png)

And the code works well while i change the provider to **CPUExecutionProvider**。

Also the ascend log file under the directory "ascend/debug" details are:
